# Image Optimization Rules

- On image addition or update:
  - Reduce image file size without quality loss.
  - Convert to WebP if applicable.
  - Suggest lazy loading (`loading="lazy"`) for large or offscreen images.
  - Check for missing alt text in related HTML.
